question: Which botanical garden can be found in Kota Bogor, Indonesia?
asked_question_translated: Kterou botanickou zahradu najdete v Kota Bogor v Indonésii?
answer: V Kota Bogor v Indonésii najdete Bogorskou botanickou zahradu.
answer_translated_eng: In Kota Bogor, Indonesia, you will find the Bogor Botanical Garden.
